poojai ( english : veneration ) is a 2014 indian tamil action masala film directed by hari and produced by vishal , who himself plays the lead role alongside an ensemble cast featuring shruti haasan , sathyaraj , raadhika sarathkumar and mukesh tiwari . yuvan shankar raja composed the soundtrack and score for the film , while cinematography and editing were handled by priyan and v. t. vijayan , respectively . the film was officially launched on 28 march 2014 and principal photography began on 18 april 2014 . the film released on 22 october 2014 on the occasion of deepavali . the film was dubbed into hindi as himmatwar and in telugu titled as pooja . it is also being remade in kannada as anjani putra starring puneeth rajkumar .